The communicated case information you should base your judgement on is as follows: The application concerns the deportation of the applicants’ family members by the Montenegrin authorities to the authorities of Republika Srpska in Bosnia and Herzegovina in May 1992, where they were later killed or went missing. The applicants complain, under procedural limb of Articles 2 and 3, about a lack of an effective investigation into the impugned event..
